Project Overview

             Official website of Baba Ghulam Shah Badshah University (BGSBU), featuring:

            University leadership profiles

            Academic departments & programs

            Campus facilities and news updates

            Administration details

            Student resources and placement information


Project Structure

├── index.html                # Homepage

├── pages/
│   ├── Administration/
│   │   └── Chancellor.html   # Chancellor's profile
│   ├── Departments/
│   │   ├── SOET         # SOET Folder
│   │       ├── Academics.html    # Academic programs
│   │       ├── Administration.html # College administration
│   │       ├── department.html   # Department listings
│   │       └── Placement.html    # Placement center
        ├── SOET.html                 # School of Engineering & Tech

├── css/
│   └── styles.css            # Custom styles

├── js/
│   ├── script.js             # Main interactions
│   └── search.js             # Search functionality

├── images/                   # All visual assets
│   ├── administration/
│   ├── campus images/
│   ├── departments/
│   ├── news/
│   └── other/

└── README.txt                # This file

Key Features

  1 Responsive Design

        Mobile-first approach

        Hamburger menu for mobile

        Fluid grid layouts

  2 Interactive Elements

        Animated dropdown menus

        Search form with suggestions

        Scroll-triggered animations (AOS)

        Image galleries with hover effects 

  3 Content Sections
       
       Leadership profiles with cards

       Department overviews

       News/Events marquee

       Campus photo gallery

       Quick links portal

  4 Technical Stack
 
    Tailwind CSS framework

    Font Awesome icons

    Google Fonts (Poppins)

    AOS (Animate On Scroll)





Third-Party Resources: Tailwind CSS (MIT)

                       Font Awesome (CC BY 4.0)

                       AOS Library (MIT)

                       Google Fonts (OFL)


Maintenance

   1 Content Updates

        Edit HTML files directly

        Update image assets in /images

        Modify styles.css for design changes

   2 Dependencies

        Keep Tailwind CSS updated

        Maintain Font Awesome kit link

        Check AOS compatibility